You can use Acumatica ERP to organize your everyday work. That is, you can add tasks and events and manage them by using the system tools. To work efficiently, you should have easy access to the list of your tasks and events. In Acumatica ERP, you can view the number of active tasks and events in the info area in the upper-right corner of the form. (For details, see [HelpRoot_Interface\Info_area|Info Area] in the Interface Guide.) For important tasks and events, you can add reminders.{br}
This chapter describes how you can manage your tasks, events, and reminders. ==In This Chapter==[anchor|#_16b0a21e-abad-4daa-8b0c-9212e2bb53a6] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#_0615b77f-4938-428c-989a-1a2f3939d35c] *[HelpRoot_GettingStarted\IB_My_Tasks_and_Events_Panel|Your Tasks and Events ] *[HelpRoot_GettingStarted\EP__con_Task_Management|Task Management] *[HelpRoot_Administration\EP__con_Notifications_About_Events|Notifications About Events]
