You can configure the modern user interface of Acumatica ERP so that all the forms and reports you use frequently in your work are at hand. In this section, you will read about ways you can personalize the modern user interface. ==In This Section==[anchor|#_295d75be-d8f7-4f30-83f8-44e49c4a650f] {| class="checklist invisiblechecklist" | width="100%" |- | [anchor|#_529585ca-c2f6-425a-87e6-ad278b3bb9a6] *[HelpRoot_GettingStarted\GS__con_Personalize_User_Interface|Personal Settings of the Modern User Interface]
